    • Income

      public Income()

    • Income

      public Income(String id, Float total, String category, String vendor, String description, User user, String userId, Date createdAt, Date updatedAt, BankAccount bankAccount, String accountId, int repeatAmount, String repeatMetric, Date repeatStart, Date repeatEnd)
      Constructs an instance of the Income class with specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      id - Unique identifier for the income.
      total - Total amount of the income.
      category - Category of the income.
      vendor - Vendor associated with the income.
      description - Description or notes about the income.
      user - User associated with this income.
      userId - Unique identifier of the user linked to this income.
      createdAt - Date when the income entry was created.
      updatedAt - Date when the income entry was last updated.
      bankAccount - Bank account associated with this income.
      accountId - Unique identifier for the linked bank account.
      repeatAmount - Number of times the income is repeated.
      repeatMetric - Time unit for repeating the income (e.g., daily, monthly).
      repeatStart - Start date for repeating the income.
      repeatEnd - End date for repeating the income.
